[{"title":"介绍","url":"/introduce/","content":"<p>欢迎进入 <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL0Jyb3duLUxlZQ==\">Brown Lee</span>! 本网站由 <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvLw==\">Hexo</span>提供搭建! 文档请阅读：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cDovL2hleG8uaW8v\">http://hexo.io</span>。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>本博客网站用于记录一些前端开发中的难点, 不可用作其他用途, 仅可用于学习交流。<br>本网站部分功能尚未开通，请尽请期待~~~。<br>如果有问题，请联系 <code>lth2508@outlook.com</code> , 投稿可联系 <code>1994756616@qq.com</code> 。</p>\n","categories":["介绍"],"tags":["简介"]},{"title":"文本超出显示省略号 功能","url":"/css/%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%BA%A2%E5%87%BA%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9C%81%E7%95%A5%E5%8F%B7/","content":"<p>涉及前端行业的小伙伴都知道基本所有公司都会多多少少的要求文本溢出显示省略号，具体怎么实现呢，下面列出几种方法:</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"单行显示省略号\"><a href=\"#单行显示省略号\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"单行显示省略号\"></a>单行显示省略号</h2><p>IE 浏览器 IE8 及以下 版本可能不支持此功能. 如 需要用到此功能，请查阅下面几种方法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"language-css\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-css\">    <span class=\"selector-class\">.box</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-css\">      <span class=\"attribute\">line-height</span>: <span class=\"number\">22px</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-css\">      <span class=\"attribute\">white-space</span>: nowrap;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-css\">      <span class=\"attribute\">overflow</span>: hidden;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-css\">      <span class=\"attribute\">text-overflow</span>: ellipsis;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-css\">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-css\">  </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span>hexo 框架简单好用，hexo 框架简单好用，hexo 框架简单好用，hexo 框架简单好用，hexo 框架简单好用<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["CSS"],"tags":["CSS","入门"]}]